wife was under
investigation.

21:35.494 --> 21:37.263 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
This is light years from that.

21:37.363 --> 21:40.366 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: John
McLaughlin, the attorney
general said today that, look,
he -- as a

21:40.466 --> 21:44.470 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
