21:57.316 --> 21:59.118 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
do.

21:59.218 --> 22:03.589 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The context here is one that of
a president
who has been elected in an
environment where

22:03.689 --> 22:08.661 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
