23:52.164 --> 23:53.999 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Michael
Mukasey, what about
that point?

23:54.099 --> 23:57.136 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
For the good of the party, for
